'''I-81''', or '''Eyeate-won''', was an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] food [[Droid/Legends|droid]] stolen from a diplomatic party by the [[The Gutterwipes]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Peekoine]] along with [[I-812]]. Both droids were only barely mobile and preferred to stay out of trouble.

